Package: autheliar
Type: Package
Title: An R wrapper for the authelia API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Liam", "Gilbey", , "liam.gilbey@gmail.com", c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Autheliar helps to provide users with an intuitive interface to the
    Authelia API. It allows R users to implement SSO authentication with the goal
    focused on providing authentication to plumber APIs and shiny applications.
